event.title: Monthly Fellowship Meeting in Linz, Austria

body.p: The FSFE Fellowship Group Linz meets in the Hackspace DevLoL, Hofgasse 19, 4020 Linz. Our meetings start at 18:30 (CEST) and the Agenda will start at 19:00 (CEST). Everyone, who is interessted in the FSFE or free Software in general is invited to come to our meeting. We are pleased to meet you there.
